      <description>&lt;p&gt;I’m currently a &lt;strong&gt;Fulbright Visiting Scholar&lt;/strong&gt; at the &lt;strong&gt;University of Pittsburgh (Pitt)&lt;/strong&gt;. I started on &lt;strong&gt;September 1, 2025&lt;/strong&gt;, and I’ll be here for &lt;strong&gt;one year&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Last week, I gave a talk at Pitt (Agora Series) titled &lt;strong&gt;“Data Privacy and Advertising: Understanding User Consent Decisions in Data-Driven Environments.”&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/pitt-agora-talk-poster.jpeg&#34; alt=&#34;Talk poster&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can see the department’s announcement here:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.linkedin.com/posts/university-of-pittsburgh-department-of-communication_hey-everyone-the-last-agora-is-on-april-activity-7445566006934007808-t5PX?utm_source=social_share_send&amp;amp;utm_medium=member_desktop_web&amp;amp;rcm=ACoAAAZuI10B6h9K3EpxslWtLjWaDOmxHIvGga0&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;LinkedIn post (University of Pittsburgh Department of Communication)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
